'''Steve Weinstein''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Awards===

* [[ACBL King or Queen of Bridge]] 1982
* ACBL Player of the Year (1) 1995

===Wins===

* [[World Open Pairs Championship]] (1) 2010
* [[Buffett Cup]] (2) 2006, 2010 
* [[Cavendish Invitational|Cavendish Invitational Pairs]] (7) 1993, 1996, 1999, 2002, 2007, 2009, 2010
* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (16)
